News.Title: Annapurna Swadisht Acquires 75% Stake in Andri Agro
News.Summary: Packaged food manufacturer Annapurna Swadisht Ltd announces acquisition of majority stake in West Bengal-based Andri Agro Foods for ₹15 crore enterprise value to enter soya-based products market.

News.Title: Annapurna Swadisht Reports 23% Growth in Quarterly Net Profit
News.Summary: Annapurna Swadisht reported consolidated net profit of 154 million rupees for Q2, compared to 125 million rupees in the same period last year. The company's revenue increased to 2.5 billion rupees from 2 billion rupees year-over-year.

News.Title: Annapurna Swadisht Proposes Acquisition of Madhur Confectioners
News.Summary: Annapurna Swadisht has announced a proposal to acquire a 100% stake in Madhur Confectioners, a company operating in the food and beverages sector. This move represents a significant corporate action aimed at expanding Annapurna Swadisht's presence in the confectionery market.
